Speaker 1: I have no idea.

Speaker 2: Okay, I can see what's going on.

Speaker 2: Last name, S-R-I-T-U-L-A.

Speaker 1: My zip code is 92346.

Speaker 2: Okay, no, that wasn't an email or a text telling you to do anything.

Speaker 1: You actually just were approved.

Speaker 2: They're going to ship your order out,

Speaker 1: and you'll receive it in about three to five business days.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: Yeah, no problem. Have a good one. Bye-bye.
